@prefix cr:   <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#> .
@prefix top:  <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#> .
@prefix owl:  <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

# ADaM analysis layer + traceability.
# ADaM's value is reproducibility: every analysis result traces to its source. In this
# reference the chain is result -> analysis dataset -> NATIVE source facts (via W3C PROV
# wasDerivedFrom), i.e. traceability to the one source of truth, not the fragile
# SDTM-document -> ADaM-document chain. SDTM and ADaM are both views of the native graph.

cr:AnalysisDataset a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf top:Evidence, top:ProvenancedEntity ;
    rdfs:label "Analysis Dataset (ADaM)" ;
    rdfs:comment "An ADaM analysis dataset (e.g. ADSL, ADAE). Must declare prov:wasDerivedFrom its source so any result built on it is reproducible to source." .
